		<div class="comment-body"><p>Hi andrew,<br />
All these snipers, or ones that are pretty close *could* theoretically appear as level 40 versions, but it seems much more likely to find perfect ones when you&#8217;re around level 69 due to the way the game&#8217;s loot engine seems to work.  Plus, the chances of getting them from the Armory or Crawmerax is much higher than anywhere else, because of the sheer volume of loot you&#8217;ll get from those sources.  For farming good snipers at level 40 though, it&#8217;s probably best to try the Crimson Fastness.  Check this out: <a href="http://www.borderlandsbestgear.com/how-to-get-borderlands-best-weapons/" rel="nofollow">http://www.borderlandsbestgear.com/how-to-get-borderlands-best-weapons/</a><br />
